text: The Vengeance of She is a 1968 British fantasy adventure movie directed by Cliff Owen and starring John Richardson, Olga Schoberová, Edward Judd, André Morrell, Colin Blakley. It was distributed by 20th Century Fox and is a loose sequel to the 1965 movie She. ==Other websites== * Category:1968 fantasy movies Category:1968 adventure movies Category:British fantasy movies Category:British adventure movies Category:20th Century Fox movies Category:Movies set in Spain
